{"tid":1591411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動Po］10.1 創意玩法","createTime":"2019-09-24T06:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:16:11.000Z","uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de05faa92508f892bd973d046f9f41d851250e33","tid":1591411,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"就係 全人拋紙錢啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMK4oy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMK4oy9.jpg&h=829ef4bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係，</span>就咁拋衣紙有啲兒戲，上到國際層面只係落佢面，睇唔到點樣同呢場運動緊扣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以，</span>我地要大嗌 同埋周圍貼 周圍寫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&lsquo;To Our Beloved Freedom, Democracy and Human Rights&rsquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n（記住五大訴求係基於民主自由人權而成）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望帶出嘅效果就係<br />\n1) 一定唔少得嘅落佢面。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2) 中共嘅來臨，就係我地香港人 自由民主人權 嘅逝去，諷刺中共嘅極權統治。<br />\n<br />\n3) Show 比世界睇香港人對 自由民主人權嘅渴求。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.1 每人一疊紙錢 賀佢老母<br />\n若果老人家唔放便落樓，叫佢千奇唔可以由上拋落黎！！<br />\n每人行多一步，每人買一堆，不做freerider。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">街頭抗爭固然重要，但要長遠走落去，一定要加多啲創意同要多元化！</span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅紅事，就係我地嘅白事；<br />\n佢嘅白事，就係我地嘅紅事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aiKv3B8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaiKv3B8.jpg&h=bfe4db0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附上一張自己9整嘅文宣。"},{"pid":"5a7137609ca96209daebf543f3d761a87afe3631","tid":1591411,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"568f989656e0e8ce8b5b8bdd6f8cde0b46d2fb61","tid":1591411,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"9連"},{"pid":"ee329c23bff61f00b6fce97c4441a578dd9ba172","tid":1591411,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"